step.action:
Update {{session_file}} with enhanced tracking:
      - Add {{task_number}} to completed_tasks array
      - Update task_status.{{task_number}}:
          status: completed
          completed_at: {{iso_timestamp}}
          progress_file: {{progress_file}}
          files_created: {{list from progress}}
          files_modified: {{list from progress}}
          exports: {{exports from progress}}
          issues: {{issues from progress}}
      - Set current_task to next incomplete task:
          - Find first task N where task_status.N.status != "completed"
          - If all tasks completed, set current_task = {{total_tasks}}
          - Else set current_task = {{next_incomplete_task}}
      - last_updated: {{iso_timestamp}}
      - status: in-progress (or "ready-for-verify" if all tasks done)

Verify all outputs were created:
      - {{progress_file}}
      - Updated {{context_handoff_file}}
      - Updated {{session_file}}
